   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1865_12_04_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>TELGE NÖLTING &amp; Co.<lb/>SHANGHAI. Shanghai, 4th December 1865<lb/>Messrs. L.
            Kniffler<lb/>Nagasaki<lb/>We have received your esteemed letter from <lb/>18th Nov. and
            have retrieved from it the remittance for <lb/>Us1656.72. 10 L. S. for Russell +
            Co.<lb/>which we credit to Mr. J. C. Julius Möller as per your <lb/>wishes, subject to
            correct receipt. <lb/>Mr. Möller will go to Nagasaki himself <lb/>by steamer._<lb/>Yours
            sincerely<lb/>Telge Nölting + Co.</p>
         <pb facs="1865_12_04_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <pb facs="1865_12_04_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1865_12_04_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_4.tif" n="4"/>
         <p>⟨1865<lb/>Telge Nölting+Co<lb/>Shanghai Dec. 4th<lb/>R[eceived] Dec. 11th<lb/>ans[wered]
            20th Dec. 65.⟩</p>
      </body>
